Package: peat-node
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 avahi-daemon
Description: Defense Unicorns Peat sidecar node (CRDT mesh sync daemon)
 Runs the peat-node binary as a systemd service. Exposes a gRPC API
 on localhost for co-located applications to read/write shared CRDT
 state that syncs across the Peat mesh over Iroh/QUIC.
 .
 Intended for Raspberry Pi field nodes in the Peat RPi test deployment.
